description: Retrieves the location of stored game session logs for a specified game session. When a game session is terminated, Amazon GameLift automatically stores the logs in Amazon S3 and retains them for 14 days. Use this URL to download the logs.  See the AWS Service Limits page for maximum log file sizes. Log files that exceed this limit are not saved.
